Package: gtscales
Title: Color Scale Extensions for 'gt'
Version: 0.0.1
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Christopher T.",
           family = "Kenny",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ctkenny@proton.me",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9386-6860"))
Description: Adds legend helpers for color-encoded 'gt' tables. The primary
    interface combines 'gt::data_color()' with matched legends for continuous,
    binned, quantile, and discrete scales, while lower-level helpers support
    legend-only and reusable scale specification workflows.
